title: Towie’s Lewis Bloor has ‘gone missing’ after Marnie Simpson brands him a ‘scumbag’ for bedding another girl behind her back on Valentine’s Day
text:
TV Magazine NO WHERE TO BE SEEN Towie’s Lewis Bloor has ‘gone missing’ after Marnie Simpson brands him a ‘scumbag’ for bedding another girl behind her back on Valentine’s Day 
Friends have voiced their concern for Lewis after revealing he's been 'unreachable' since the clip emerged Exclusive By SARAH PACKER, Bizarre Reporter 22nd February 2017, 11:45 am
